public class AppointmentOutcomeDetail extends AppointmentOutcome
The AppointmentOutcomeDetail class extends AppointmentOutcome, providing detailed information about an appointment outcome, including the associated appointment and any prescribed medications.

      Constructs an AppointmentOutcomeDetail with the specified details, including prescriptions and appointment details.
      Parameters:
      id - The unique ID of the appointment outcome.
      patientId - The ID of the patient associated with this outcome.
      appointmentId - The ID of the appointment associated with this outcome.
      serviceType - The type of service provided during the appointment.
      consultationNotes - Notes from the consultation, describing the outcome.
      createdAt - The date and time when this outcome was created.
      updatedAt - The date and time when this outcome was last updated.
      prescriptions - An array of prescriptions issued during the appointment.
      appointment - The detailed appointment associated with this outcome.
